<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١/ ١/ ٣٨٣)</span> و<span class="c1">"تهذيب الكمال"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ٢٠٤)</span> و<span class="c1">"تهذيبه"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٤٨٠)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وأما ابنه وهو بشر بن بكر فله ترجمة في <span class="c1">"ميزان الإعتدال"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٣١٤)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
